  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study was to identify neural correlates involved in arthmetics processing in
      adults and children aged 8 to 14 with normal cognitive function. Brain area will be
      identified by functional magnetic resonance imaging (IRMf).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
